content:
When your transaction contains outdated prices, the Transaction Line Editor displays a warning. If necessary, your sales reps can refresh the prices or manually update the Validation Status field to submit the transaction.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Unlimited, Enterprise, and Developer editions for Industries clouds where Revenue Lifecycle Management is enabled.

How: In the warning message above the Transaction Line Editor, click Refresh Prices.
title: Refreshing Inaccurate Prices in Salesforce
